{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n512\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 1\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 1\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 405 + 9 + 2 = 416\u2081\u2080\n\n772\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 567 + 63 + 2 = 632\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n416 \u00d7 632 = 416 \u00d7 (600 + 32)\n= 416 \u00d7 600 + 416 \u00d7 32\n= 249,600 + 13,312\n= 262,912\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n262912 \u00f7 9 = 29212 r 4\n29212 \u00f7 9 = 3245 r 7\n3245 \u00f7 9 = 360 r 5\n360 \u00f7 9 = 40 r 0\n40 \u00f7 9 = 4 r 4\n4 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 4\n\nReading from bottom to top: 440574\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n440574\u2089 = 4\u00d759049 + 4\u00d76561 + 0\u00d7729 + 5\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 4\u00d71\n= 236196 + 26244 + 0 + 405 + 63 + 4\n= 262,912\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n**440574**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 471}